CustomField.description: This field is optional. It is populated manually within the risk rating worksheet. This field should not be edited directly. This field stores the manually populated override risk grade if one is set int he risk rating worksheet. If this value is populated, this value will be used to calculate the final risk grade instead of the calculated risk grade. If a user sets a overriden risk grade within the risk rating worksheet. they are required to add a comment.
CustomField.label: Overridden Risk Grade Value
